{"tid":2306830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.31太子站事件15個月   英國旗婆婆到現場獻花","createTime":"2020-11-30T17:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T17:07:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"21b1ff57b01f8a9bc524af12e0f9e53a160b2225","tid":2306830,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/VkfFF8NP/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FVkfFF8NP%2Fimage.jpg&h=821bbf18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31太子站事件發生至今15個月，有市民到太子站外打算獻花或致意，大批警員下午起在現場一帶戒備，並在站外圍上橙色膠帶。<br />\n<br />\n警方透過揚聲器表示，現場人士可能違反4人限聚令的規定，要求他們離開，大批記者在場拍攝採訪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1562831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1562831&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=825db8b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1562831&h=cc9616c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1562831</a>"}]}